  "texts": [
    "This review explores generative AI's potential in orthopedics education and training, focusing on prospects like personalized learning, interactive case studies, and accessible resources.",
    "It then discusses hurdles associated with its adoption like accuracy, bias, and the importance of human expertise.",
    "Finally, it explores the road ahead for research, curriculum integration, and ethical considerations.",
    "By providing a structured overview of the applications and challenges associated with generative AI, this review aims to serve as a roadmap for educators as well as researchers interested in advancing orthopedic education through AI-driven innovations.",
    "Section 1 of this paper provides an overview of the various forms and techniques of generative AI."
  ],
